First we check if the root is null, if it is null then we consider that as mirror and return true.
We create two queue, one for the left side another for the right side.
We push root->left in queue Left and root->right in queue Right
while Left not empty and Right not empty:
We first Take the front(x from Left,y from Right) from both queues and pop them.
if both X and Y both are Null we continue
if only either of them are null, we return false.
if the value of x and y dont match, we return false
We push x->left then x->right in Left
We push y->right then y->left in Right.

After the while loop runs out, we return Left.empty() and Right.empty()
